Official setup instructions link: https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/setup/linux

Step 1: https://code.visualstudio.com/download

Step 2: Go to the folder the file has been downloaded and open a terminal

Step 3: use this command sudo apt install ./<file>.deb   (change <file> with the file name)

Step 4: Install gcc compiler if not installed
				Command sudo apt install gcc
				check if install with: gcc --version
				
Step 5: install C/C++ and Code Runner Extension.




Optional

To Work with Input Output file

Step 1: Create two files with name "input.txt" and "output.txt" in the same folder

Step 2: Go to terminal -> configure Tasks

Step 3: Change the tasks.json file with the given file
